elements.name: Verifying Book hotel including GST_card(debit card_VISA) with special request

steps.name: User is on the OMR Branch hotel page
User should verify sucess message after login "Welcome Kanagaraj"
User enters the search details "Tamil Nadu","Chennai","Deluxe","2-Two","1-One" and "2"
User should verify search hotel after success message "Select Hotel"
User selects the first hotel name and save the name,price
User should verify its success message after select hotel "Book Hotel"
User add the guest details "Mr.","kanak","raj","9894982610" and "gvkanagaraj@gmail.com"
User add the GST details "9043592058","Greens Tech OMR Branch" and "Thoraipakkam" and click Next
User add the special request "Add bonfire"
User add the payment details,proceed with card type "<Card Type>"
User should verify after booking "Booking is Confirmed" and save the order id
User should verify same selected Hotel is present

name: Verifying OMR Branch Book hotel Details Automation
